{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-work-template-js","path":"/wcrs/","result":{"data":{"page":{"id":"f8e62269-3990-5971-8aae-724fe388c747","html":"<p>During my tenure at WCRS, I was involved in several brainstorms, promotional ideas, internal projects, hack evenings, small microsites and games. Some of them include:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Creative work to promote on mobile phones the new electric <a href=\"https://www.bmw.co.uk\">BMW</a>’s i3</li>\n<li>Creative work for <a href=\"https://www.bupa.com/\">Bupa</a>’s health services</li>\n<li>Brainstorming and conceptualisation of ideas for a <a href=\"https://www.royalnavy.mod.uk/\">Royal Navy</a> project</li>\n<li>A Google Maps hack to retrieve directions from point A to B</li>\n<li>A Wordpress plugin adaptation to capture the details of candidates for the WCRS work experience program</li>\n<li>An internal newsletter template regarding Social Media</li>\n<li>What should they call it? A small microsite to find out the best name for the new royal baby</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/fb05eac6904f630be4b429ffee5fd8ce/dbdff/1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"1\"\n        src=\"/static/fb05eac6904f630be4b429ffee5fd8ce/dbdff/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/fb05eac6904f630be4b429ffee5fd8ce/d1f95/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/fb05eac6904f630be4b429ffee5fd8ce/dbdff/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n      